      public String type
      Extension type. Please note that legacy 'Department' extension type corresponds to 'Call Queue' extensions in modern RingCentral product terminology Enum: User, FaxUser, FlexibleUser, VirtualUser, DigitalUser, Department, Announcement, Voicemail, SharedLinesGroup, PagingOnly, IvrMenu, ApplicationExtension, ParkLocation, DelegatedLinesGroup, GroupCallPickup
